observe these photons

00:09:11.790 --> 00:09:15.630
at microwave frequencies, and
at a temperature of about 2.7

00:09:15.630 --> 00:09:17.570
Kelvin.

00:09:17.570 --> 00:09:21.140
So I thought they would
