calculations and they

00:10:35.620 --> 00:10:40.920
predicted that there should be
a signal of about 3 Kelvin being

00:10:40.920 --> 00:10:44.000
coming from the Big Bang.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.140
There were two
disconnected groups.

00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:51.870
One of them had no idea
about the CMB expectations.

00:10:51.870 --> 00:10:57.260
